			(property "Description" "BME280 - Combined Digital Humidity and Pressure Sensor\n\nCharacteristics:\n\n• Vcc: 1.8V ~ 3.3V\n•  Pressure Range: 300 ~ 1100 mBar\n•  Pressure Resolution: 0.0015 mBar, max\n•  Pressure Accuracy: relative &plusmn;0.12 mBar, abs &plusmn; 1 mBar\n• Humidity Resolution: 0.008% RH, max\n• Humidity Accuracy: &plusmn;3% RH\n• Temperature Resolution: 0.01°C\n• Temperature Accuracy: 0.5°C\n• Operating Temperature: -40°C to 85°C\n\nDigikey:\n\n828-1063-1-ND"
